{"tid":1411935,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家公司 為左可以阻止大家罷工可以去到幾盡","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:59.000Z","uid":78604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80f622d44af7c8ccb32d0d2df3febe1a7387535e","tid":1411935,"uid":78604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"等細佬我拋磚引玉 講左自己先<br />\n<br />\n首先介紹下我老闆<br />\n<a href=\"https://stp.stheadline.com/columnist_pen/columnist_content.php?columnist_id=40&amp;id=2861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstp.stheadline.com%2Fcolumnist_pen%2Fcolumnist_content.php%3Fcolumnist_id%3D40%26id%3D2861&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEJX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=efdd0984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstp.stheadline.com%2Fcolumnist_pen%2Fcolumnist_content.php%3Fcolumnist_id%3D40%26id%3D2861&h=1a7242ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://stp.stheadline.com/columnist_pen/columnist_content.php?columnist_id=40&amp;id=2861</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係我老闆架一篇文章：<br />\n其實，如果通過修訂「逃犯條例」，我認為對香港的樓市帶來好處，第一 : 香港是一個國際金融中心，資金可以自由進出香港，犯罪集團利用香港成為洗黑錢、恐怖活動融資的地方，透過購買物業，轉售後變成白錢或作恐怖活動用途，修訂後黑錢流走，減少假需求，降低樓市被扭曲的機會。第二 : 國內貪汚情況嚴重，貪官為避免失勢後財產充金，紛紛將資金移入香港，就算面對辣招，繳付三成的印花稅亦面不改容，通過修訂有助大陸捉拿貪官，並充公他們的資產，減少走資入香港，香港的樓市才可健康發展。第三 : 美國加了9次息，香港只加0.125厘，原因大量黑錢或不法得來的資金流入香港，銀行的銀根鬆動，難以加息，通過修訂對黑錢有阻嚇作用，銀行資金緊張，拆息向上，加息亦遏止樓價上升，減少對物業的需求，樓價有望回落。<br />\n中國的資金是推高香港樓價的幕後黑手，辣招已不能有效地減少需求，只有從源頭根治，所以如果通過修訂「逃犯條例」，比辣招更有效控制樓市。可是，政治大於社會公義，香港將繼續成為逃犯天堂，大家只有無可奈何。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3E47rZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3E47rZ.png&h=5cb3856d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而呢一位就係我架上司<br />\n佢每位同事親自打過去 話如果今日邊個冇返工<br />\n就會通知老闆 相當上心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T49gYzH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT49gYzH.png&h=fbdfcd46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3F0FN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3F0FN3.png&h=b0787181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老闆就咁on9啦 唔知大家老闆又會點做呢"},{"pid":"694bf47bbfbf1c22d1ad2bca99ba07c8c32a5b95","tid":1411935,"uid":78604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d49f0dea2e783cac8dea2ec081584cc2db6de8d","tid":1411935,"uid":78604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94f378bc4159b1a622df67ceee5e9a62e183e8a5","tid":1411935,"uid":67153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"唔好推啦<br />\nHide漏名呀"},{"pid":"636978cfb33eb332ee1231372b60d803e25aa3fc","tid":1411935,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"老細就無咩, 反而有個19同事係一個group叫大家一齊唔返, 另一個group就叫人下晝返, 真係盡見人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779cccf56edbdd5755e8c131819eb7c3640b1b18","tid":1411935,"uid":231408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"「緊急」5/8出屯門嘅全部同我入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411986</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cfa70bf3a303cf2a1c68bf326fb377a2da42a46a","tid":1411935,"uid":78604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636978cfb33eb332ee1231372b60d803e25aa3fc","tid":1411935,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"老細就無咩, 反而有個19同事係一個group叫大家一齊唔返, 另一個group就叫人下晝返, 真係盡見人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"老細有冇講啲咩先"}]}